		●參考書資料暨網路資源 Reference Books and Online Resources教師提供之課堂討論參考資料


三、教學目標 Objectives


本課程為教育學程之通識課程，旨在介紹學習策略之發展，創造力對學習與教學的重要性，以及學習策略在實務上之應用。課程目標有︰1.透過瞭解學習策略與創造力，在專業學習奠定良好基礎2.透過團隊合作進行創造力專案實作3.瞭解自己的生涯規劃與定位，從而培養屬於自己的學習策略技能 


This course is designed for general education in teacher education program. The main purpose of this course is to reveal the development of learning strategies, the importance of creativity learning/teaching, and the practical of learning strategies. The goal of this course including: 1) Understanding the learning strategies and creativity in order to build the foundation of professional learning, 2) Participating the group creativity project, 3) Discovering the career setting/plan and developing personal learning strategie. 


