本論文永久網址:      Twitter研究生:黎瓊麗研究生(外文):Li, Chiung-Li論文名稱:國小學童英語學習動機、學習策略與學習成就之相關性研究：以屏東地區國小為例論文名稱(外文):The Study of Elementary School Children's English Learning Motivation, Learning Strategy and Learning Achievement: An Analytical Case of Pingtung County指導教授:劉慶中、鍾榮富指導教授(外文):Liu, Cing-Jhong、Jhong, Rong-Fu學位類別:博士校院名稱:國立屏東師範學院系所名稱:教育行政研究所學門:教育學門學類:教育行政學類論文出版年:2005畢業學年度:93語文別:中文論文頁數:337中文關鍵詞:國小英語教學、學習動機、學習策略、學習成就外文關鍵詞:English Eduaction in Elementary School、Learning Motivation、Learning Strategy、Learning Achievement相關次數:

被引用:240點閱:7295評分:下載:2550書目收藏:86



國小學童英語學習動機、學習策略與學習成就之相關性研究：以屏東地區國小為例摘要本研究的目的在於探討屏東縣國小六年級學生英語學習動機、英語學習策略與英語學習成就之間的關係，以及屏東縣國小六年級學生的英語學習動機、英語學習策略是否因性別、學習環境不同而有顯著差異。本研究以文獻分析設計英語學習動機量表及英語學習策略量表，並以問捲調查方式取得受試者的基本資料、英語學習動機及學習策略之資料，以受試者上網測試方式取得其英語學習成就之資料，並以訪談方式取得受訪者之英語學習經驗之看法與意見。本研究的主要研究發現如下：一、 不同性別小六學生在英語學習動機上有部分差異二、 不同性別小六學生在英語學習策略上有部分差異。三、 不同性別小六學生在英語學習成就上有顯著差異。四、 不同性別小六學生在英語學習環境上有部分差異。五、 不同學習環境之小六學生在英語學習動機上有部分差異。六、 不同學習環境之小六學生在英語學習策略上有部分差異。七、 不同學習環境之小六學生在英語學習成就上有部分差異。八、 小六學生的英語學習動機與英語學習成就具有顯著正相關。九、 小六學生的英語學習策略與英語學習成就具有顯著正相關。十、 小六學生的英語學習動機對英語學習成就具有顯著的解釋力。十一、 小六學生的英語學習策略對英語學習成就具有顯著的解釋力。十二、 小六學生的英語學習動機與英語學習策略對英語學習成就具有顯著的解釋力。本研究的結論如下：一、 性別在英語學習動機的部分層面上具有明顯差異。二、 性別在英語學習策略的部分層面上具有明顯差異。三、 性別在英語學習成就上有明顯差異。四、 性別在英語學習環境的部分層面上具有明顯差異。五、 學習環境在英語學習動機的部分層面上具有明顯差異。六、 學習環境在英語學習策略的部分層面上具有明顯差異。七、 學習環境在英語學習成就上部分具有明顯差異。八、 英語學習動機與英語學習成就具有顯著正相關。九、 英語學習策略與英語學習成就具有顯著正相關。十、 英語學習動機對英語學習成就具有顯著的解釋力。十一、 英語學習策略對英語學習成就具有顯著的解釋力。十二、 英語學習動機與學習策略對英語學習成就具有顯著的解釋力。本研究針對研究發現與結論，對國小英語教育與未來研究提出以下的建議：一、 就家長而言：宜多關心子女的英語學習狀況，可提高男生在「期望價值」及「工具性」層面的學習動機，並降低「被動性」層面的學習動機，及提高女生在「記憶策略」及男生在「補償策略」及「社會策略」的使用頻率二、 就英語教師而言，宜積極與學生建立良好的師生關係，加強學生的「期望價值」、「工具性」、「自我效能」及「被動性」學習動機，並增加學生學習策略各層面的使用頻率三、 就行政人員而言：宜積極延攬正試英語師資及充實學校設備。四、 就學習者而言：宜提高「期望價值」、「工具性」及「自我效能」層面的學習動機，並增加「社會策略」、「認知策略」及「記憶策略」的使用頻率，及建立良好的師生關係與同儕關係五、 就未來研究而言：可增加變項、運用不同研究工具、擴大研究對象及採用不同的研究方法。關鍵詞：國小英語教學、學習動機、學習策略、學習成就

The Study of Elementary School Children’s English Learning Motivation, Learning Strategy and Learning Achievement—An Analytical Case of Pingtung CountyAbstract    English Education in Elementary School was a global tendency and it wasone of our government’s policies.  The purposes of this study were to understand the relation of sixth-grade students’ English learning motivation, English learning strategy, and English achievement in Pingtung County, and to understand whether those sixth-grade students’ English learning motivation, English learning strategy had any difference in gender and learning environment.The findings of this study were as follows:1. The students’ English learning motivation had some difference in gender.2. The students’ English learning strategy had some difference in gender.3. The students’ English achievement had significant difference in gender.4. The students’ English learning environments had some difference in gender.5. The students in different English learning environments had some difference in English learning motivation.6. The students in different English learning environments had some difference in English learning strategy.7. The students in different English learning environments had some difference in English achievement.8. The students’ English learning motivation and English achievement had a positive relation.9. The students’ English learning strategy and English achievement had a positive relation.10. The students’ English learning motivation could explain their English achievement significantly.11. The students’ English learning strategy could explain their English achievement significantly.12. The students’ English learning motivation and English learning strategy could explain their English achievement significantly.The conclusions of this study were as follows:1. The students’ English learning motivation, strategy, environments and achievement had significant differences in gender.2. The students’ English learning motivation, strategy, and achievement had significant differences in English learning environments.3. The students’ English learning motivation and achievement had a positive relation.4. The students’ English learning strategy and achievement had a positive relation.5. The students’ English learning motivation could explain their achievement significantly.6. The students’ English learning strategy could explain their achievement significantly.7. The students’ English learning motivation, and strategy could explain their achievement significantly.The suggestions of this study were as follows:1. Parents should care about children’s learning and promote children’s learning motivation, learning strategy and improve children’ learning environments.2. English teachers should have good relation with students, especially with male students.  English teachers should get an official license as soon as possible and promote students’ learning motivation and strategy.3. School Administrators should improve learning environments for students and hire licensed English teachers.4. Students should promote their learning motivation and strategy, and they also should have good relation with teachers and peers to help them learn English.5. The researcher could add different variables to the research frame, have participants from other counties, use different research tools, and add different research methods in the future study.Keywords: English Education in Elementary School, Learning Motivation, Learning Strategy, Learning Achievement

